-<p>输出对应位置的网络信号值，如果网络信号未覆盖到，也输出0。</p> 
-<p>一个网格如果可以途径<a class="hl hl-1" data-pretit="不同的" data-report-click="{&quot;spm&quot;:&quot;1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;dest&quot;:&quot;https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;extra&quot;:&quot;{\&quot;searchword\&quot;:\&quot;不同的\&quot;}&quot;}" data-report-view="{&quot;spm&quot;:&quot;1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;dest&quot;:&quot;https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;extra&quot;:&quot;{\&quot;searchword\&quot;:\&quot;不同的\&quot;}&quot;}" data-tit="不同的" href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020" target="_blank">不同的</a>传播衰减路径传达，取较大的值作为其信号值。</p>
