-<h2><a name="t1"></a><a id="_4"></a>题目描述</h2> 
-<p>给出一个<a class="hl hl-1" data-pretit="二叉树" data-report-click="{&quot;spm&quot;:&quot;1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;dest&quot;:&quot;https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%91&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;extra&quot;:&quot;{\&quot;searchword\&quot;:\&quot;二叉树\&quot;}&quot;}" data-tit="二叉树" href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%91&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020" target="_blank">二叉树</a>如下图所示：</p>
-<p><img alt="image-20240219094626190" src="https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/blog_migrate/e899db1af92a3e9322b4e82b478339c1.png"></p>
-<p>请由该二叉树生成一个新的二叉树，它满足其树中的每个节点将包含原始树中的左子树和右子树的和。</p> 
-<p><img alt="image-20240219094722295" src="https://i-blog.csdnimg.cn/blog_migrate/4224171f6a2711c1716bfd92ad39359d.png"></p>
-<p>左子树表示该节点左侧叶子节点为<a class="hl hl-1" data-pretit="根节点" data-report-click="{&quot;spm&quot;:&quot;1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;dest&quot;:&quot;https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E6%A0%B9%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;extra&quot;:&quot;{\&quot;searchword\&quot;:\&quot;根节点\&quot;}&quot;}" data-tit="根节点" href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E6%A0%B9%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020" target="_blank">根节点</a>的一颗新树；右子树表示该节点右侧叶子节点为根节点的一颗新树。</p>
-<h2><a name="t2"></a><a id="_18"></a>输入描述</h2> 
