-<h2><a name="t1"></a><a id="_4"></a>题目描述</h2> 
-<p>给定一个<a class="hl hl-1" data-pretit="字符串" data-report-click="{&quot;spm&quot;:&quot;1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;dest&quot;:&quot;https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;extra&quot;:&quot;{\&quot;searchword\&quot;:\&quot;字符串\&quot;}&quot;}" data-tit="字符串" href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020" target="_blank">字符串</a>s，找出这样一个子串：</p>
-<ol><li>该子串中任意一个字符最多出现2次</li><li>该子串不包含指定某个字符</li></ol> 
-<p>请你找出满足该条件的<a class="hl hl-1" data-pretit="最长子串" data-report-click="{&quot;spm&quot;:&quot;1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;dest&quot;:&quot;https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B2&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020&quot;,&quot;extra&quot;:&quot;{\&quot;searchword\&quot;:\&quot;最长子串\&quot;}&quot;}" data-tit="最长子串" href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B2&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.7020" target="_blank">最长子串</a>的长度</p>
-<h2><a name="t2"></a><a id="_13"></a>输入描述</h2> 
-<p>第一行为：要求不包含的指定字符，为单个字符，取值范围[0-9a-zA-Z]</p> 
-<p>第二行为：字符串s，每个字符范围[0-9a-zA-Z]，长度范围[1, 10000]</p> 
-<h2><a name="t3"></a><a id="_20"></a>输出描述</h2> 
