-<p>输入</p> 
-<pre class="set-code-show prettyprint" data-index="0"><code class="has-numbering" onclick="mdcp.copyCode(event)" style="position: unset;">2,2
-10,20
-30,40
-<div class="hljs-button {2}" data-title="复制"></div></code><ul class="pre-numbering" style=""><li style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">1</li><li style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">2</li><li style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">3</li></ul></pre> 
-<p>输出</p> 
-<pre class="set-code-show prettyprint" data-index="1"><code class="has-numbering" onclick="mdcp.copyCode(event)" style="position: unset;">70
-<div class="hljs-button {2}" data-title="复制"></div></code><ul class="pre-numbering" style=""><li style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">1</li></ul></pre> 
-<p>说明</p> 
-<blockquote> 
- <p>行走的路线为：右→下</p> 
-</blockquote> 
